data.description: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity in the Redlands with NO HOA! Located in a peaceful, family-oriented neighborhood just minutes from the Florida Keys, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a gem. Inside, you'll find recent upgrades like LVP flooring, a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, and a brand-new tankless Titan water heater. Enjoy hurricane-impact windows, a professionally maintained in-ground pool, spacious backyard with mango trees and a beautiful Quonset hut and fire pit area for entertaining on those chilly nights. The property also offers a new A/C unit, a large laundry area with mudroom access to the backyard, a reverse osmosis water filtration system, ample parking space for your boat or RV, and a new fence. Schedule a showing today!
